snippet.title: How Did Johnny Depp Lose To Amber Heard?! - A Lawyer Reacts to Shocking Libel Verdict for The Sun
snippet.description:
The verdict is in on Johnny Depp's libel case against british tabloid The Sun and accusations by Amber Heard. As someone who has followed the case, I was shocked that Johnny lost. So I brought in Lawyer & Comedian Lindsay Glazer to help me breakdown how this happened... What this means for Johnny and more.  #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
